						<a itemprop="replyToUrl" data-entry-pid='1448194' href='http://forums.phpfreaks.com/topic/281815-robot-detection-class-for-your-use/#entry1448194' rel='bookmark' title='Robot Detection Class - For Your Use: post #13'>
					
